title: Democratic Rep. Jasmine Crockett launches bid for U.S. Senate in Texas
description: Democratic Rep. Jasmine Crockett launched her campaign Monday for the U.S. Senate in Texas, a critical race for Democrats hoping to reclaim the Senate majority in the 2026 midterm elections.
